Please respect the format which was agreed on. The prefix consisting of an acronym is written for BOTH teams: (FC) FCSB and (CSA) Steaua Bucuresti. This is not the place to write their common short names, which are FCSB and Steaua. The whole point of this article is to make clarifications and to reduce confusion. We don't achieve this by erasing critical information, like their names.
